		     =-=-=- Tinker -=-=-=

	Tinkers are the blacksmiths and weaponsmiths of the
MUD. They forge weapons and armours with metal ingots found
in mines. These weapons are oftimes much more powerful than
any item which can be found on mobs or in areas, as are the 
armours as well. 

Type:   Blacksmithing Warrior
Skills: some combat/specialized forging skills
Spells: None
Prime Attributes: Dex, Str

Examples: Pick any blacksmith in history who also knew how
	to fight _____.
Comments: These guys can forge /SICK/ items. They charge
	a heck of a lot for their services.
